            "title": "Zabbix-Grafana图形展示软件",
            "date_published": "2021-09-14T10:08:48.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"下载grafana-rpm包\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#下载grafana-rpm包\">#</a> 下载 grafana rpm 包</h2>\n<pre><code># 下载Rpm包\nwget https://dl.grafana.com/oss/release/grafana-7.4.0-1.x86_64.rpm\n# 安装grafana\nsudo yum install -y grafana-7.4.0-1.x86_64.rpm\n# Grafana安装zabbix插件\ngrafana-cli plugins install alexanderzobnin-zabbix-app\n# 安装饼状图\ngrafana-cli plugins install grafana-piechart-panel\n# 开机自启\nsystemctl enable grafana-server\n# 启动\nsystemctl start grafana-server\n地址:ip:3000\n# Grafana Zabbix插件配置数据源\nURL:http://localhost/api_jsonrpc.php\n</code></pre>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Centos",
                "安全管理",
                "数据可视化",
                "监控",
                "运维",
                "Zabbix"
            ]
